Updated PR so that by default search is performed in `records*` indices.

I still left the `index` parameter for the search API in case there is a need to manually specify which index we want to search on. This makes sense for example on INSPIRE where we don't need to search across 1M records when all we want is to do a search in Conferences or Jobs. 

