If you put the following code into a notebook cell, it will put a small PNG in that cells output area:

```json
%%javascript
var output = {
    data: {
        "image/png": ""
    },
    output_type: "display_data"
};
this.append_output(output);
```

The `this` variable in this context is the `OutputArea` object for that cell. This gives you full access to the output of that cell in a programmatic API.

